          "R5"
        ],
        "comments": [
          {
            "text": "The next step is to move the king along the 7th rank instead of going back to the 6th rank.\n\nThis way, Black loses a tempo!\n\nBareev resigned here, but let's see how the game would have continued.",
            "arrows": null,
            "highlights": null
